<h1 id="text">Why Should You volunteer</h1>
<p id="Why">People choose to volunteer for a variety of reasons. For some it offers the chance to give something back to the community or make a difference to the people around them. For others it provides an opportunity to develop new skills or build on existing experience and knowledge.
    Regardless of the motivation, what unites them all is that they find it both challenging and rewarding.</p>
<div class="container1">
<form action="/volunteer/new" method="post">
        <div class="contact-box">
            <div class="left"></div>
            <div class="right">
                <h1 id="volunteer">Volunteer with us</h1>
                <input type="text" class="field" placeholder="Your Name" name="name">
                <input type="email" class="field" placeholder="Your Email" name="email">
                <input type="text" class="field" placeholder="Your Phone" name="phone">
                <textarea class="field area" placeholder="Suggest Something to help us improve" name="message"></textarea>
                <button type="submit" class="btn1">Send</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        </form>
    </div>
{{/partial}}
{{>layout.hbs}}
<style>
 *{
   padding: 0;
     margin: 0;
     box-sizing: border-box;
<!--     font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;-->
 }
 .container1{
     position:relative;
     display: flex;
     justify-content: center;
     align-items: center;
     width: 100%;
     height: 100%;
     padding: 20px 100px;
     font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
 }
 .container1:after{
     content:"";
     position: absolute;
     left:0;
      top: 0;
     width:100%;
     height:650px;
          background:url(https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/wbm.thumbnail/dissolve/1200/703860.jpg) no-repeat center ;
     background-size: cover;
     z-index: -1;
    filter: blur(10px)
 }
.contact-box{
    max-width: 1000px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr);
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 19px 5px  rgba(0,0,0,0.19);
    margin-top: 80px;
}

.left{
    height: 100px;
    background: url(https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/wbm.thumbnail/dissolve/1200/703860.jpg) no-repeat center;
    background-size: cover;
    height: 550px;
}
.right{
    padding:25px 40px
}
#volunteer{
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}
volunteer:after{
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left:50px;
    bottom: 0;
    transform: translate(110px);
    height: 4px;
    width:50px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background-color: #2ecc71;
}
.field{
    width:100%;
    padding:0.5rem 1rem;
    outline: none;
    border: 2px solid rgba(0,0,0,0);
    background-color:rgba(230,230,230,0.6);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    transition: 3s;

}
.field:hover{
    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
.field:focus{
    background-color: #fff;
    border:2px solid rgba(30,85,250,0.47);

}
.area{
    min-height:150px;
}
.btn1{
    width:100%;
    padding:0.5rem 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    background-color:#2ecc71;
    cursor: pointer;
    outline:none;
    border:none;
    color:#fff;
    transition:3s;
}
.btn1:hover{
background-color:#27ae60;
}
#text{
text-align:center;
font-size:50px;
}
#Why{
text-align:center;
font-size:20px;
margin-left:70px;
margin-right:70px;
}
@media screen and (max-width:800px){
    .contact-box{
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .left{
        height: 200px;
    }
}

</style>
